  "description": "Web 模型铁路（N 轨）轨道设计工具。SCARM 风格的拖近吸附 + 角度校正自动连接，纯浏览器运行。",
  "license": "MIT",
  "homepage": "https://maplefirecn-prog.github.io/toyrail_planner/",
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "git+https://github.com/maplefirecn-prog/toyrail_planner.git"
  },
  "bugs": {
    "url": "https://github.com/maplefirecn-prog/toyrail_planner/issues"
  },
  "scripts": {
    "serve": "node tools/serve.js",
    "check": "node --check src/app.js && node --check tools/serve.js && node --check tools/smoke_test.js",
    "smoke": "node tools/smoke_test.js http://127.0.0.1:8765/",
    "browsers:install": "playwright install chromium",
    "test": "npm run check"
